This '''timeline of Apple Inc. products''' is a list of all stand-alone [[Apple II]], [[Apple Macintosh|Macintosh]], and other computers, as well as computer peripherals, expansion cards, ancillary products, and consumer electronics sold by [[Apple Inc.]] This list is ordered by the release date of the products. {{Timeline of Apple Inc. products}}
